; Regression test for issue #716: Need a better error for automated transactions with null amounts (BZ#716)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/716
; An automated transaction posting with no amount should produce a clear error.

= /Expenses/
    Savings:Auto

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
While applying automated transaction from "$FILE", lines 5-6:
> = /Expenses/
>     Savings:Auto
While extending transaction from "$FILE", lines 8-10:
> 2024/01/01 Test
>     Expenses:Food    $10.00
>     Assets:Cash
Error: Automated transaction's posting has no amount
end test
